s_synopsis: Keep your head down. Concentrate. Release a ton of power coming out of your backswing - like a coiled spring! Follow through. You'll need a picture-perfect swing, flawless timing and a pro's club selection. Why, you ask? Because this is real. The traps are real, the water is real, the ball is real. And your score is real. So real, you'll save green fees and a tip for the caddy!
